{"tid":2178784,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【習總小康夢碎】洪災重創9省市 國務院：逾200萬人受災、1.3萬戶恐變回貧窮","createTime":"2020-08-28T15:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T15:38:29.000Z","uid":339805,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6beb0ddd1db46e532361c55c3be1d3fabe118b1a","tid":2178784,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:21:01.000Z","msg":"內地天災不斷，武漢肺炎疫情尚未結束，又暴雨成災。 國務院扶貧開發領導小組辦公室副主任洪天雲坦言，自入汛以來，截至本月21日，安徽等9個省市出現嚴重洪澇災害，涉及296個貧困縣、1.5萬個貧困村，受災民眾超過200萬人，其中1.3萬戶恐變回貧窮戶，再挫國家主席習近平曾提出「2020年實現全民脫貧」的小康夢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/HYKBW3LDWVFILCZ35SVQZMFGDM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2huwtGPv4oDaFphp67eOSTiOZMbYN0OGh4puEnVeBzzDWB1lJVAyJmAdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FHYKBW3LDWVFILCZ35SVQZMFGDM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2huwtGPv4oDaFphp67eOSTiOZMbYN0OGh4puEnVeBzzDWB1lJVAyJmAdg&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyMyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=930e9248\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FHYKBW3LDWVFILCZ35SVQZMFGDM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2huwtGPv4oDaFphp67eOSTiOZMbYN0OGh4puEnVeBzzDWB1lJVAyJmAdg&h=1520259d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/HYKBW3LDWVFILCZ35SVQZMFGDM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2huwtGPv4oDaFphp67eOSTiOZMbYN0OGh4puEnVeBzzDWB1lJVAyJmAdg</a>"},{"pid":"926957e564752cce7eb8839dfe604c7cf87b5540","tid":2178784,"uid":118120,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:24:36.000Z","msg":"習總: 你地唔好拖國家後腿<br />\n年尾仲要消滅全國貧窮<b